<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<!--
%\VignetteEngine{knitr::knitr_notangle}
%\VignetteIndexEntry{Label Abbreviation Workflow}
%\VignetteEncoding{UTF-8}
-->
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<style type="text/css">
body { max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; line-height: 1.55; }
pre { background: #f6f8fa; padding: 0.9rem; overflow-x: auto; }
code { font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Menlo, Consolas, monospace; }
</style>
<title>Label Abbreviation Workflow</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Label Abbreviation Workflow</h1>

<p>这个 vignette 展示 <code>asciiwright</code> 里最顺手的一条标签工作流：</p>

<ol>
<li>先预览智能缩写结果</li>
<li>再手工修改你不满意的标签</li>
<li>把这些修改转成 <code>label_overrides</code></li>
<li>最后再生成 ASCII Wright map</li>
</ol>

<h2>准备数据</h2>

<!--begin.rcode setup
library(asciiwright)

pdat <- example_polytomous_data()
labels <- pdat$items
labels
end.rcode-->

<h2>第一步：预览缩写</h2>

<p><code>preview_label_abbrev()</code> 会同时给出建议缩写和最终缩写。此时如果还没传 <code>label_overrides</code>，<code>suggested</code> 和 <code>final</code> 会一致。</p>

<!--begin.rcode preview
preview <- preview_label_abbrev(
  labels,
  width = 18,
  style = "smart",
  side = "item"
)

preview
end.rcode-->

<h2>第二步：手工调整</h2>

<p>你可以直接在 preview 表里修改 <code>final</code> 这一列。下面把两个标签改得更贴近实际报告里的写法。</p>

<!--begin.rcode edit
preview$final[preview$label == "Read books on animals"] <- "Read books animals"
preview$final[preview$label == "Find where animal lives"] <- "Animal habitat"

preview
end.rcode-->

<h2>第三步：生成 overrides</h2>

<p><code>make_label_overrides()</code> 会把 preview 表里的差异提取成一个命名字符向量，这个对象可以直接传给 <code>wright_map_ascii()</code>、<code>polytomous_range_map_ascii()</code> 等函数。</p>

<!--begin.rcode overrides
overrides <- make_label_overrides(preview)
overrides
end.rcode-->

<h2>第四步：出图</h2>

<p>现在把 <code>label_abbrev = "smart"</code> 和刚生成的 <code>label_overrides</code> 一起传进去。</p>

<!--begin.rcode render
map_custom <- wright_map_ascii(
  persons = pdat$persons,
  items = pdat$items,
  person_display = "distribution",
  label_width = 18,
  name_trunc = 18,
  label_abbrev = "smart",
  label_overrides = overrides
)

cat(as.character(map_custom))
end.rcode-->

<h2>Range map 里按列定制</h2>

<p>如果你想对不同列分别定制标签，可以让 <code>label_overrides</code> 变成一个函数。对于 range map，<code>side</code> 会区分 <code>"item_bottom"</code>、<code>"item_center"</code> 和 <code>"item_top"</code>。</p>

<!--begin.rcode range
range_map <- polytomous_range_map_ascii(
  persons = pdat$persons,
  items = pdat$items[1:2],
  steps = pdat$steps,
  person_display = "distribution",
  item_display = "labels",
  item_width = 18,
  name_trunc = 18,
  label_abbrev = "smart",
  label_overrides = function(label, width, side) {
    if (side == "item_bottom") return(paste("Bottom", label))
    if (side == "item_center") return(paste("Center", label))
    if (side == "item_top") return(paste("Top", label))
    label
  }
)

cat(as.character(range_map))
end.rcode-->

<h2>小结</h2>

<ul>
<li>如果你希望大部分标签自动缩写，只对少数标签人工修正，这条工作流会很顺手。</li>
<li>如果你想先预览缩写效果，确认对齐和可读性后再正式出图，这条工作流也很适合。</li>
</ul>

<p>如果后续你打算把这套缩写固定到项目里，直接把 <code>overrides</code> 保存成脚本里的一个命名向量就可以反复复用。</p>

</body>
</html>
